        <Parent_String>armed forces [300137540], organizations (groups) [300025948], Organizations (hierarchy name) [300234770], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
